                81,707 次收藏</div></div></div></div><div class="Card FollowshipCard"><div class="NumberBoard FollowshipCard-counts NumberBoard--divider"><a type="button" class="Button NumberBoard-item Button--plain" href="/org/hu-wai-tan-xian-za-zhi/following"><div class="NumberBoard-itemInner"><div class="NumberBoard-itemName">关注了</div><strong class="NumberBoard-itemValue" title="6">6</strong></div></a><a type="button" class="Button NumberBoard-item Button--plain" href="/org/hu-wai-tan-xian-za-zhi/followers"><div class="NumberBoard-itemInner"><div class="NumberBoard-itemName">关注者</div><strong class="NumberBoard-itemValue" title="54029">54,029</strong></div></a></div></div><div class="Card"><a class="Profile-createOrgAccount" target="_blank" href="https://www.zhihu.com/org/signup">开通机构号</a></div><div class="Profile-lightList"><a class="Profile-lightItem" target="_blank" href="/lives/users/c87408d027c25ed16bac8dc00768ac07"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">举办的 Live ⚡️</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">4</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/org/hu-wai-tan-xian-za-zhi/following/topics"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的话题</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">10</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/org/hu-wai-tan-xian-za-zhi/following/columns"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的专栏</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">0</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/org/hu-wai-tan-xian-za-zhi/following/questions"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的问题</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">154</span></a></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><div id="data" style="display:none" data-state="{&quot;common&quot;:{&quot;ask&quot;:{}},&quot;privacy&quot;:{&quot;showPrivacy&quot;:false},&quot;loading&quot;:{&quot;global&quot;:{&quot;count&quot;:0},&quot;local&quot;:{&quot;people/get/&quot;:false,&quot;people/getActivities/hu-wai-tan-xian-za-zhi&quot;:false}},&quot;entities&quot;:{&quot;users&quot;:{&quot;hu-wai-tan-xian-